          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Enriched targets were used. The degree of enrichment",
                "was 78-95%. For Fe and Co targets were made of metallic",
                "foils mounted on tantalum backing. The remaining",
                "targets were prepared from powders of ZnO and NiO",
                "enriched in the appropriate isotope. The powers were",
                "deposited in a uniform layer on a tantalum substrate",
                "and were pressed between the substrate-base and a",
                "platinum foil 0.02-0.05 mm thick. The  target",
                "thicknesses were 11-34 mg/cm**2."
